metadata.name: ‘’DIVERSE’’
metadata.description: Diverse is an NFT project which consists of 5000 hand-crafted, lifelike art pieces. We take global prospectives and reflect them in our project which promotes diversity, equality and inclusion. The variations includes 5 main male and female figures, each with their own unique ethnicities that showcase the truly diverse cultural roots of the earth we inhabit together. Diverse is a community-driven project focused on encapsulating our diverse world and bringing individuals together that make the Earth a beautiful place!
